    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for your next adventure? This well-maintained vehicle is in good condition and offers a smooth, reliable ride that you can count on! It\u2019s been cared for with attention to detail, making it a fantastic choice for anyone looking for a dependable car with plenty of great miles ahead. Come see why this solid performer is the perfect fit for your daily drive!",
